int main()
{
    int a;
    printf("\n enter number:");
    scanf("%f",&a);
    if(a<0)
        printf("\n number is negative.");
    else if(a>0)
        printf("\n number is positive");
    else
        printf("\n number is zero");
}


Output:
enter number:
5

 number is positive

OR
enter number:
0

 number is zero

OR
enter number:

-45

 number is negative.

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-check-number-is-positive.html
